<h2>How does it work?</h2>
<p>Some games allow OpenID login. Using your own OpenID identity, you can start playing the game in one single click.</p>
<p>Just click the Direct Play link in the game overview and start playing right away.</p>

<h2>Where can I get an OpenID?</h2>
<p>Surpise! You may already have one. There are a lot of popular OpenID providers. You might already have an OpenID identity with one of these providers!</p>
<p>Click <a href="http://openid.net/get/" target="_BLANK">here</a> for more information.</p>
